<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
    <title>ChamaOS — Services</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/app.css" />
    <style>
      .hero-with-bg {
        background-image: url("/images/ChamaOSLandingpage.jpg");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-attachment: fixed;
        position: relative;
      }
      .hero-with-bg::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(
          135deg,
          rgba(11, 79, 108, 0.75),
          rgba(244, 185, 66, 0.15)
        );
        z-index: 1;
      }
      .container-overlay {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('../partials/header', { brandTagline: 'Community savings. Built together.' }) %>

    <main class="container">
      <section
        class="card hero hero-with-bg"
        style="
          min-height: 500px;
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
        "
      >
        <div class="container-overlay" style="max-width: 1000px; width: 100%">
          <div class="hero-content" style="text-align: center; color: #fff">
            <h1 class="h1" style="color: #fff">
              ChamaOS — community finance made simple
            </h1>
            <p class="lead" style="color: #fff; opacity: 0.95">
              A warm, trustworthy platform for chamas to collect contributions,
              manage records and celebrate shared milestones — designed for
              groups that save together.
            </p>
            <div class="hero-ctas" style="justify-content: center">
              <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/signup"
                >Get started — create a chama</a
              >
              <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/login">Sign in</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="features-grid" style="margin-top: 32px">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="feature-icon">👥</div>
          <div class="small">Group management</div>
          <h3 class="h2">Create & manage chamas</h3>
          <p class="small">
            Define groups, roles and contribution schedules with simple controls
            and clear permissions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="feature-icon">📝</div>
          <div class="small">Contribution tracking</div>
          <h3 class="h2">Records & reminders</h3>
          <p class="small">
            Automatic contribution tracking, reminders and receipts — all
            exportable for audits and transparency.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
          <div class="small">Milestones</div>
          <h3 class="h2">Celebrate progress</h3>
          <p class="small">
            Track goals, schedule payouts and reward members when the group
            reaches financial milestones.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🔒</div>
          <div class="small">Security</div>
          <h3 class="h2">Safe & auditable</h3>
          <p class="small">
            Role-based access, clear audit logs and exportable reports keep
            funds and relationships secure.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
          <div class="small">Insights</div>
          <h3 class="h2">Simple analytics</h3>
          <p class="small">
            Clear dashboards and quick reports to help chamas understand growth
            and plan their next steps.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🤝</div>
          <div class="small">Community</div>
          <h3 class="h2">Connect & grow</h3>
          <p class="small">
            Forums, events and shared milestones help groups learn from one
            another and strengthen trust.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="service-section">
        <h2 class="h1">All services at a glance</h2>

        <div class="card" style="margin-top: 16px">
          <h3 class="service-title">Group & Member Management</h3>
          <ul class="service-list">
            <li>Create and invite members to chamas</li>
            <li>Define group rules, contribution amounts and schedules</li>
            <li>Assign roles: admin, treasurer, member, auditor</li>
            <li>Flexible permissions and approval workflows</li>
            <li>Member profiles with contribution history</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-top: 16px">
          <h3 class="service-title">Contribution & Payment Tracking</h3>
          <ul class="service-list">
            <li>Automatic payment reminders and due dates</li>
            <li>Record, verify and confirm contributions</li>
            <li>Digital receipts & transaction history</li>
            <li>Export records for audits and tax purposes</li>
            <li>Payment status dashboard by member</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-top: 16px">
          <h3 class="service-title">Financial Goals & Milestones</h3>
          <ul class="service-list">
            <li>Set and track group savings goals</li>
            <li>Schedule and automate payouts to members</li>
            <li>Milestone celebrations with member notifications</li>
            <li>Transparent fund allocation & distribution</li>
            <li>Goal progress dashboards</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-top: 16px">
          <h3 class="service-title">Analytics & Reporting</h3>
          <ul class="service-list">
            <li>Group savings trends and growth metrics</li>
            <li>Member contribution analysis</li>
            <li>Gender, location and demographic breakdowns</li>
            <li>Customizable reports and exports (CSV, PDF)</li>
            <li>Admin dashboards with real-time KPIs</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-top: 16px">
          <h3 class="service-title">Security & Trust</h3>
          <ul class="service-list">
            <li>Role-based access control (RBAC)</li>
            <li>Comprehensive audit logs of all actions</li>
            <li>Data encryption and secure storage</li>
            <li>Community guidelines enforcement</li>
            <li>Anonymous reporting for disputes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-top: 16px">
          <h3 class="service-title">Community Features</h3>
          <ul class="service-list">
            <li>Group forums and discussion boards</li>
            <li>Member-to-member messaging</li>
            <li>Event scheduling and coordination</li>
            <li>Knowledge sharing and best practices</li>
            <li>Celebrate wins and group achievements</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="card cta-left">
          <h3 class="h2">Ready to start?</h3>
          <p class="small">
            Join ChamaOS today and bring your group's savings to life. Create a
            chama in under a minute.
          </p>
          <div class="cta-action">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/signup">Create a chama now</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-side">
          <div class="card small">
            Have questions? <a class="link-muted" href="#">Contact support</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <!--footer-->
      <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
